ow-reverse;'><div>عَلِيمٌ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> ٤٥ إِنَّمَا وَلِيُّكُمُ ٱللَّهُ وَرَسُولُهُۥ وَٱلَّذِينَ ءَامَنُواْ ٱلَّذِينَ </div><div>يُقِيمُونَ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>ٱلصَّلَوٰةَ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> وَيُؤۡتُونَ ٱلزَّكَوٰةَ وَهُمۡ رَٰكِعُونَ ٥٥ وَمَن يَتَوَلَّ ٱللَّهَ </div><div>وَرَسُولَهُۥ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>وَٱلَّذِينَ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> ءَامَنُواْ فَإِنَّ حِزۡبَ ٱللَّهِ هُمُ ٱلۡغَٰلِبُونَ ٦٥ يَٰٓأَيُّهَا ٱلَّذِينَ </div><div>ءَامَنُواْ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>لَا</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> تَتَّخِذُواْ ٱلَّذِينَ ٱتَّخَذُواْ دِينَكُمۡ <a data-content='سخرية وهزلا ومُجونا' tabindex='0' role='button' class='fake-link tafsir' data-toggle='popover' data-placement='top'>هُزُوٗا وَلَعِبٗا</a> مِّنَ ٱلَّذِينَ </div><div>أُوتُواْ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.5vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>ٱلۡكِتَٰبَ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> مِن قَبۡلِكُمۡ وَٱلۡكُفَّارَ أَوۡلِيَآءَۚ وَٱتَّقُواْ ٱللَّهَ إِن كُنتُم مُّؤۡمِنِينَ </div><div>٧٥</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'></div>",
